RawLine: TNPC_60078462,「獨憐幽草澗邊生，上有黃鸝深樹鳴。春潮帶雨晚來急，野渡無人自橫。」是漏了哪一字呢？,「独怜幽草涧边生，上有黄鹂深树鸣。春潮带雨晚来急，野渡无人自横。」是漏了哪一字呢？

Items.mt: "I feel sorry for the grass that grows by the edge of the river, on which the yellowbird sings in the deep trees. The spring tide brings rain in the evening, and no one is crossing the wilderness. Which word is missing?
